🤖 Chat AI Application

A modern, full-stack Chat AI Application built using SmolAgents (Hugging Face) and powered by the Moonshot AI – Kimi-K2.5 model. 
This application delivers intelligent, context-aware conversations with a clean and responsive user interface.

🚀 Features
💬 Real-time AI chat interface
🧠 Context-aware responses using advanced LLM (Kimi-K2.5)
🤖 Agent-based architecture using Hugging Face SmolAgents
⚡ Fast and scalable API integration
🎨 Modern UI built with React & Material UI
🔄 Seamless frontend-backend communication
📱 Responsive design

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend
React.js
Material UI (MUI)
JavaScript (ES6+)
Backend
Python
FastAPI / Flask (depending on your setup)
SmolAgents (Hugging Face)

AI Model
moonshotai/Kimi-K2.5 (via API)
